#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module is designed to help users who have difficulty hearing audible "
"cues, or who have difficulty using a keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul je oblikovan, da pomaga uporabnikom, ki imajo težave z zaznavanjem "
"zvočnih namigov ali težave z uporabo tipkovnice ali miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The module is divided into six tabs: <link linkend=\"access-bell"
"\"><guilabel>Bell</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-modifier-keys"
"\"><guilabel>Modifier keys</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-"
"keyboard-filters\"><guilabel>Keyboard Filters</guilabel></link>, <link "
"linkend=\"access-activation-gestures\"><guilabel>Activation Gestures</"
"guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"mouse-navigation\"><guilabel>Mouse "
"Navigation</guilabel></link>, and <link linkend=\"access-screenreader"
"\"><guilabel>Screen Reader</guilabel></link>."
msgstr ""
"The module is divided into six tabs: <link linkend=\"access-bell"
"\"><guilabel>Zvonec</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-modifier-keys"
"\"><guilabel>Modifikacijske tipke</guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"access-"
"keyboard-filters\"><guilabel>Filtri Tipkovnice</guilabel></link>, <link "
"linkend=\"access-activation-gestures\"><guilabel>Aktivacijske geste</"
"guilabel></link>, <link linkend=\"mouse-navigation\"><guilabel>Navigacija z "
"miško</guilabel></link>, in <link linkend=\"access-screenreader"
"\"><guilabel>Bralec Ekrana</guilabel></link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bell"
msgstr "Zvonec"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This panel is divided into an <guilabel>Audible Bell</guilabel> section and "
"a <guilabel>Visible Bell</guilabel> section."
msgstr ""
"Ta pult je razdeljena na razdelka <guilabel>Slišni Zvonec</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Vidni Zvonec</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top check box labeled <guilabel>Use System Bell</guilabel>, determines "
"whether the normal System bell rings. If this option is disabled, the System "
"bell will be silenced."
msgstr ""
"Vrhnje potrditveno polje <guilabel>Uporabi sistemski zvonec</guilabel>, "
"določa ali naj sistemski zvonec zvoni. Če je ta možnost onemogočena, bo "
"sistemski zvonec brez glasu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next check box down can be used to play a different sound whenever the "
"system bell is triggered. To activate, place a mark in the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Use customized bell</guilabel>, and enter the complete pathname to "
"the sound file in the text box labeled <guilabel>Sound to play</guilabel>. "
"If you want, you can select the <guibutton>Browse</guibutton> button to "
"navigate through your filesystem to find the exact file."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje potrditveno polje se lahko uporablja za predvajanje različnih "
"zvokov, kadar je sistemski zvonec že sprožen. Da aktivirate to možnost, "
"odkljukajte potrditveno polje z oznako <guilabel>Uporabi prilagojeni zvonec</"
"guilabel> in vnesite celotno pot do zvočne datoteke v vnosno polje z oznako "
"<guilabel>Predvajaj zvok</guilabel>. Če želite, lahko izberete gumb "
"<guibutton>Brskaj</guibutton>, da prebrskate skozi vaš datotečni sistem in "
"najdete pravo datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For those users who have difficulty hearing the System bell, or those users "
"who have a silent computer, &kde; offers the <emphasis>visual bell</"
"emphasis>. This provides a visual signal (inverting the screen or flashing a "
"color across it) when the system bell would normally sound."
msgstr ""
"Za tiste uporabnike, ki imajo težave s poslušanjem sistemskega zvonca, ali "
"za tiste, ki imajo tih računalnik, &kde; ponuja <emphasis>vizualni zvonec</"
"emphasis>. Ta zagotavlja vizualni signal (obračanje zaslona ali utripanje "
"barve na zaslonu), ko bi se običajno oglasil sistemski zvonec."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use the visual bell, first place a mark in the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Use visual bell</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Da uporabite vidni zvonec, najprej odkljukajte potrditveno polje z oznako "
"<guilabel>Uporabi vizualni zvonec</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can then select between <guilabel>Invert screen</guilabel>, or "
"<guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel>. If you select <guilabel>Invert screen</"
"guilabel>, all colors on the screen will be reversed. If you choose "
"<guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel>, you can choose the color by clicking the "
"button to the right of the <guilabel>Flash screen</guilabel> selection."
msgstr ""
"Potem lahko izbirate med <guilabel>Obrni barve</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Utripaj</guilabel>. Če izberete <guilabel>Obrni barve</guilabel>, "
"bodo vse barve na zaslonu obrnjene. Če izberete <guilabel>Utripaj</"
"guilabel>, lahko izberete barvo z gumbom na desni strani razdelka "
"<guilabel>Utripaj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The spin box can be used to adjust the duration of the visible bell. The "
"default value is 500 msec, or half a second."
msgstr ""
"S poljem za vrtenje lahko prilagodite trajanje vidnega zvonca. Privzeta "
"vrednost je 500 msec ali pol sekunde."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modifier keys"
msgstr "Modifikacijske tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are the two sections <guilabel>Sticky Keys</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Locking Keys</guilabel> to this panel."
msgstr ""
"Na tem pultu sta dva razdelka <guilabel>Trajne tipke</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Ključavnice</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Sticky Keys"
msgstr "Uporabi trajne tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you can press and release the &Shift;, &Alt; or "
"&Ctrl; keys, and then press another key to get a key combo (example: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Del;</keycombo> could be done with "
"&Ctrl;, then &Alt; and then &Del;)."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, lahko uporabnik pritisne in izpusti tipke "
"&Shift;, &Alt; ali &Ctrl;, ter potem pritisne drugo tipko, da dobi "
"kombinacijo (primer: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt; &Del;</keycombo> "
"se lahko naredi s &Ctrl;, potem &Alt; in &Del;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also in this section is a check box labeled <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</"
"guilabel>. If this check box is enabled, the &Alt;, &Ctrl; and &Shift; keys "
"stay <quote>selected</quote> until you <quote>de-selected</quote> them."
msgstr ""
"Tudi v tem razdelku je potrditveno polje z oznako <guilabel>Zakleni trajne "
"tipke</guilabel>. Če je to potrditveno polje omogočeno, bodo tipke &Alt;, "
"&Ctrl; in &Shift; ostale <quote>izbrane</quote> dokler ne bodo ponovno "
"<quote>od-izbrane</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "As an example:"
msgstr "Na primer:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "With <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</guilabel> disabled:"
msgstr "Z onemogočenim <guilabel>Zakleni trajne tipke</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Shift; key then press the <keycap>F</keycap> key, the "
"computer interprets this as <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Now if you type a <keycap>P</keycap>, the computer "
"interprets this as the letter p (no shift)."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete &Shift;, nato tipko <keycap>F</keycap>. Računalnik to prevede "
"v <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Če sedaj "
"vtipkate <keycap>P</keycap>, bo računalnik razumel to kot črko p (brez "
"shift)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "With <guilabel>Lock Sticky Keys</guilabel> enabled:"
msgstr "Z omogočenim <guilabel>Zakleni trajne tipke</guilabel>:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you press the &Shift; key <emphasis>twice</emphasis> then press the "
"<keycap>F</keycap> key, the computer interprets this as <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Now if you type a <keycap>P</"
"keycap>, the computer interprets this as the letter P (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>). To de-select the &Shift; "
"key, press it again."
msgstr ""
"Če pritisnete tipko &Shift; <emphasis>dvakrat</emphasis> in nato pritisnete "
"tipko <keycap>F</keycap>, računalnik to razume kot <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Če sedaj vnesete <keycap>P</"
"keycap>, računalnik to razume kot črko P (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
"<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo>). Če želite od-zbrati tipko &Shift;, jo znova "
"pritisnite."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Filters"
msgstr "Filtri za tipkovnico"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179 index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two sections to this panel."
msgstr "Na tem pultu sta dva razdelka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use slow keys"
msgstr "Uporabi počasne tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you must hold the key down for a specified length "
"of time (adjustable with the spin box) before the keystroke will be "
"accepted. This helps prevent accidental key strokes."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, morate tipko držati pritisnjeno določen čas "
"(nastavljiv z vrtilnim okencem), preden bo pritisk tipke sprejet. S tem "
"preprečite naključne pritiske tipk."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use bounce keys"
msgstr "Uporabi skakajoče tipke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, you must wait for a specified length of time "
"(configurable with the spin box) before the next key press can be accepted. "
"This prevents accidental multiple key strokes."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, morate počakati določen čas (nastavljiv z "
"okencem za vrtenje), preden se lahko sprejme naslednji pritisk tipke. To "
"preprečuje nenamerne večkratne pritiske tipk."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Activation Gestures"
msgstr "Aktivacijske geste"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Activation Gestures</guilabel> with these options:"
msgstr "<guilabel>Aktivacijske geste</guilabel> s temi možnostmi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use gestures for activating sticky keys and slow keys"
msgstr "Uporaba gest za aktiviranje lepljivih tipk in počasnih tipk"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can activate keyboard gestures that turn on the following features:"
msgstr "Tu lahko aktivirate geste tipkovnice, ki vklopijo naslednje funkcije:"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Keys: Press &Shift;+NumLock"
msgstr "Tipke miške: Pritisnite &Shift;+NumLock"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sticky keys: Press &Shift; key 5 consecutive times"
msgstr "Trajne tipke: pritisnite tipko &Shift; 5-krat zapored"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slow keys: Hold down &Shift; for 8 seconds"
msgstr "Počasne tipke: Pridržite &Shift; za 8 sekund"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Turn sticky keys and slow keys off after a certain period of inactivity"
msgstr "Izklop trajnih in počasnih tipk po določenem času neaktivnosti"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Notification</guilabel> with these options:"
msgstr "<guilabel>Obvestilo</guilabel> s temi možnostmi:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the system bell whenever a gesture is used to turn an accessibility "
"feature on or off"
msgstr ""
"Uporaba sistemskega zvonca, kadar se z gesto vklopi ali izklopi funkcija "
"dostopnosti"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show a confirmation dialog whenever a keyboard accessibility feature is "
"turned on or off"
msgstr ""
"Prikaz pogovornega okna za potrditev, kadar je vklopljena ali izklopljena "
"funkcija za dostopnost tipkovnice"

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, &kde; will show a confirmation dialog whenever a "
"keyboard accessibility feature is turned on or off."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena,&kde; prikaže potrditveno pogovorno okno ob vsakem "
"vklopu ali izklopu funkcije dostopnosti tipkovnice."

#. Tag: member
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ensure you know what you are doing if you uncheck it, as the keyboard "
"accessibility settings will then always be applied without confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da veste, kaj počnete, če okno odznačite, bodo nastavitve "
"dostopnosti tipkovnice vedno uporabljene brez potrditve."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use &kde;'s system notification mechanism whenever a keyboard accessibility "
"feature is turned on or off"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite&kde; mehanizem sistemskega obveščanja ob vklopu ali izklopu "
"funkcije za dostopnost tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Configure Notifications</guibutton> button to open a "
"dialog which allows you to edit the notifications for status changes of all "
"keys."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb <guibutton>Konfiguracija obvestil</guibutton>, da odprete "
"pogovorno okno, ki omogoča urejanje obvestil o spremembah stanja vseh tipk."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Navigation"
msgstr "Navigiranje z miško"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab allows you to configure the keyboard number pad keys as a mouse-"
"type device. This may be useful when you are working on a device without "
"another pointing device, or where you have no other use for the number pad."
msgstr ""
"Ta zavihek omogoča konfiguracijo tipk številčnice na tipkovnici kot naprave "
"tipa miška. To je lahko koristno, kadar delate na napravi brez druge kazalne "
"naprave ali kadar nimate druge možnosti uporabe številčnice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move pointer with keyboard (using the num pad)"
msgstr "Premikanje kazalca s tipkovnico (z uporabo številske tipkovnice)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable keyboard mouse mode, you need to select the check box labeled "
"<guilabel>Move pointer with keyboard (using the num pad)</guilabel>. When "
"you do this, the other settings will become enabled, and you can customize "
"the keyboard pointer behavior further, if required."
msgstr ""
"Da omogočite način miške s tipkovnico, morate izbrati potrditveno polje z "
"oznako <guilabel>Premikanje kazalca s tipkovnico (z uporabo številčnice)</"
"guilabel>. Ko to storite, bodo omogočene druge nastavitve in po potrebi "
"lahko dodatno prilagodite obnašanje kazalca na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The various keys on the number pad move in the direction you would expect. "
"Note that you can move diagonally as well as up, down, left and right. The "
"<keycap>5</keycap> key emulates a click to a pointer button, typically "
"&LMB;. You change which button is emulated by using the <keycap>/</keycap> "
"key (which makes it &LMB;), <keycap>*</keycap> key (which makes it &MMB;) "
"and <keycap>-</keycap> (which makes it &RMB;). Using the <keycap>+</keycap> "
"emulates a double click to the selected pointer button. You can use the "
"<keycap>0</keycap> key to emulate holding down the selected pointer button "
"(for easy dragging), and then use the <keycap>.</keycap> to emulate "
"releasing the selected pointer button."
msgstr ""
"Različne tipke na številčnici se premikajo v pričakovani smeri. Upoštevajte, "
"da se lahko premikate po diagonali ter navzgor, navzdol, levo in desno. "
"Tipka <keycap>5</keycap> posnema klik na kazalčni gumb, običajno &LMB;. "
"Spreminjanje posnemane tipke, storite s tipkami <keycap>/</keycap> (s tem "
"postane &LMB;), <keycap>*</keycap> (s tem postane &MMB;) in <keycap>-</"
"keycap> (s tem postane &RMB;). Uporaba <keycap>+</keycap> posnema dvojni "
"klik na izbrani gumb kazalca. S tipko <keycap>0</keycap> lahko posnemate "
"držanje izbrane kazalne tipke (za lažje vlečenje), nato pa s tipko <keycap>."
"</keycap> posnemate sprostitev izbrane kazalne tipke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acceleration delay"
msgstr "Zakasnitev pospeševanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the time (in milliseconds) between the initial key press and the "
"first repeated motion event for mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""
"To je čas (v milisekundah) med začetnim pritiskom na tipko in prvim "
"ponovljenim dogodkom gibanja za pospeševanje tipke miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Repeat interval"
msgstr "Interval ponavljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the time in milliseconds between repeated motion events for mouse "
"key acceleration."
msgstr ""
"To je čas v milisekundah med ponavljajočimi se dogodki gibanja za "
"pospeševanje tipke miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Acceleration time"
msgstr "Čas pospeševanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the time in milliseconds before the pointer reaches a maximum speed "
"for mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""
"To je čas v milisekundah, preden kazalec doseže največjo hitrost za "
"pospeševanje tipke miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Maximum speed"
msgstr "Največja hitrost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the maximum speed in pixels per second the pointer can reach for "
"mouse key acceleration."
msgstr ""
"To je največja hitrost v slikovnih pikah na sekundo, ki jo lahko doseže "
"kazalec pri pospeševanju tipke miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pointer acceleration"
msgstr "Pospešek kazalke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the amount of acceleration to apply to mouse key acceleration."
msgstr "To je količina pospeška, ki se uporabi za pospeševanje tipke miške."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screen Reader"
msgstr "Bralnik zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:335
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Install a screen reader application like <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Orca_(assistive_technology)\">Orca</ulink> together with "
"<application>speech-dispatcher</application>."
msgstr ""
"Namestite aplikacijo za branje zaslona, kot je <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Orca_(assistive_technology)\">Orca</ulink>, skupaj z "
"<application>speech-dispatcher</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Test that sound from speech dispatcher works using the command <command>spd-"
"say hello</command> in a terminal."
msgstr ""
"Preizkusite, ali zvok iz govornega dispečerja deluje, z ukazom <command>spd-"
"say hello</command> v terminalu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition you need a text to speech synthesizer like &eg; "
"<application>espeak</application>."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega potrebujete sintetizator besedila v govor, kot je &eg; "
"<application>espeak</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable the screen reader in the checkbox, logout and restart your desktop "
"session."
msgstr ""
"V potrditvenem polju omogočite bralnik zaslona, se odjavite in znova "
"zaženite sejo namizja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For &plasma; itself, make sure to use the traditional <guilabel>Application "
"Menu</guilabel>, and check that this menu has a keyboard shortcut associated "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>). When "
"pressing this shortcut, the menu should open and be read when navigating the "
"menu with the arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"Za sam program &plasma; uporabite tradicionalni <guilabel>Meni aplikacij</"
"guilabel> in preverite, ali ima ta meni povezano bližnjico na tipkovnici "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F1</keycap></keycombo>). Ko "
"pritisnete to bližnjico, se mora odpreti meni, ki ga lahko preberete pri "
"premikanju po meniju s smernimi tipkami."

